(273, 49, 35, 'Breman Kuntanase Aboakyer 2025', '', 30, 0, '2025-11-25 18:12:46', '2025-11-25 18:12:46'),
(274, 50, 37, 'BUEST FOREX TRADER OF THE YEAR', 'This award recognizes an exceptional trader who has demonstrated outstanding skill, discipline, and consistency throughout the year. The recipient of this award stands out for their ability to analyze the markets with precision, manage risk effectively, and deliver remarkable trading performance over time.\r\nThe Best Trader of the Year embodies excellence, professionalism, and a deep understanding of market behavior. This individual showcases not only impressive profitability but also strong decision-making, emotional control, and a commitment to continuous growth. Their trading journey serves as an inspiration to others and reflects the highest standards of dedication and mastery in the financial markets.', 32, 0, '2025-11-25 23:29:34', '2025-11-25 23:29:34'),
