(239, 37, 50, 'GOMEY MAWULI', 'T3701', NULL, 'GOMEY MAWULI ,With seven years of dedicated experience in the financial markets, this trader has built a strong reputation for precision, discipline, and consistency. Their journey began with a deep curiosity about market movement and has evolved into a highly refined skill set grounded in technical analysis, price action, and strategic risk management.Over the years, they have navigated multiple market conditions—from high volatility to steady trends—developing a trading style that blends patience with sharp analytical insight. Their commitment to continuous learning, data-driven decisions, and emotional control has allowed them to deliver steady results and adapt to ever-changing market dynamics.Beyond personal performance, this trader is passionate about sharing knowledge, inspiring upcoming traders, and promoting responsible trading practices. Their seven-year track record stands as proof of resilience, growth, and mastery—making them a respected figure in the trading community.', 0, 1, 32, '2025-11-25 23:29:34', '2025-11-25 23:29:34'),
